Feature:: Add hours
    Description: Add hours worked on an activity in a project
    Actor: Employee
    
# Main scenario
Scenario: Employee adds worked hours to an activity
    Given there is a project
    And employee with ID "mkr" is logged in
    And employee is part of project
    And project has the activity "act1"
    When add "5" hours to activity in project
    Then "5" hours is added to activity in project
    
# Alternative scenario
Scenario: Employee attempts to add worked hours to an activity that does not exist
    Given there is a project
    And employee with ID "mkr" is logged in
    And project does not have the activity "act1"
    When
    Then
    
    